{"id":232711127,"title":"為什麼你會買這樣商品?動腦寒假學生營隊教你最符時下趨勢的行銷","content":"試著想想上一件你購買的商品...\n天底下商品這麼多 你為什麼會決定購買呢?\n有想過為什麼你會看到這則商品廣告嗎?\n或者是你有沒有過\n一開始打算買的不是這個商品 卻被廣告帶著走 \n最後購物車就多了好幾項東西了呢?\n這一切 都是透過\"數據\"與\"數位工具\"去做到的\n\nhttp://i.imgur.com/N3YKR4r.jpg\n\n2020動腦寒假學生營隊\n \"集結吧！數位行銷探索隊\"多元數位化行銷培訓營\nhttps://www.accupass.com/go/2020assemble\n要透過業師的六堂系統化課程+實際產品提案競賽\n讓你在一周內學習最新、最符時下趨勢的行銷方式\n更有機會獲得優渥的獎勵\n報名參加這次營隊\n讓你學習數據與數位工具是如何讓行銷變得更有力！","excerpt":"試著想想上一件你購買的商品...，天底下商品這麼多 你為什麼會決定購買呢？有想過為什麼你會看到這則商品廣告嗎？或者是你有沒有過，一開始打算買的不是這個商品 卻被廣告帶著走，最後購物車就多了好幾項東西了","anonymousSchool":false,"anonymousDepartment":true,"pinned":false,"forumId":"2bb20844-07ec-41d3-830f-ae551fc31246","replyId":null,"createdAt":"2019-12-18T09:25:33.987Z","updatedAt":"2019-12-18T09:25:33.987Z","commentCount":0,"likeCount":0,"tags":[],"topics":["寒假","競賽","行銷","獎金","大學生"],"supportedReactions":null,"withNickname":false,"reportReason":"","hiddenByAuthor":false,"meta":{"layout":"classic"},"forumName":"課程","forumAlias":"course","school":"國立高雄應用科技大學","replyTitle":null,"gender":"M","personaSubscriptable":null,"reactions":[],"hidden":false,"customStyle":null,"isSuspiciousAccount":false,"layout":"classic","withImages":true,"withVideos":false,"media":[{"url":"http://i.imgur.com/N3YKR4r.jpg"}],"reportReasonText":"","mediaMeta":[{"id":"b1c9fc8d-511c-47a5-b007-eec15af4f422","url":"https://i.imgur.com/N3YKR4rl.jpg","normalizedUrl":"https://i.imgur.com/N3YKR4rl.jpg","thumbnail":"https://i.imgur.com/N3YKR4rl.jpg","type":"image/thumbnail","tags":["ANNOTATED"],"createdAt":"2019-12-18T09:25:33.987Z","updatedAt":"2019-12-18T09:25:33.987Z"},{"id":"b1c9fc8d-511c-47a5-b007-eec15af4f422","url":"http://i.imgur.com/N3YKR4r.jpg","normalizedUrl":"https://imgur.com/N3YKR4r","thumbnail":"https://i.imgur.com/N3YKR4rl.jpg","type":"image/imgur","tags":["ANNOTATED"],"createdAt":"2019-12-18T09:25:33.987Z","updatedAt":"2019-12-18T09:25:33.987Z"}],"postAvatar":""}